      "description": "Presenting an echelon-grade example of automotive engineering: a pristine 911 Carrera S featuring the 3.8L direct-injection flat-six. This unit exhibits zero mechanical lash, with the PASM dampers providing surgical damping control and a factory-spec limited-slip differential ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The drivetrain remains in showroom-sealed condition, delivering linear power delivery through the entire RPM band. The chassis maintains its original torsional rigidity, free from any fatigue or subframe stress. A true collector\u2019s specimen for the enthusiast who demands uncompromising mechanical integrity and a flawless service pedigree.",
